value:
1. 1st Steel Foundry in India to get ISO:9002 Certification; 

2. An ISO:9001-2015 Company certified by TUV NORD, Germany (for Quality);

3. An ISO:14001-2015 Company certified by TUV NORD, Germany (for Environment); 

4.. An ISO 45001:2018 Company certified by TUV NORD, Germany (for Occupational Health & Safety); 

5.. An EN 9100:2018 certified by TUV NORD, Germany    (for Aerospace);

6. An ISO/IEC 17025:2017 certified by NABL( National Accreditation board for testing & calibration laboratory)

